Class AbstractStyleImpl

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.BasicEObjectImpl
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms.styles.impl.AbstractStyleImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, AbstractStyle
public abstract class AbstractStyleImpl extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl implements AbstractStyle
An implementation of the model object 'Abstract Style'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Background
  • Foreground
  • Line Width
  • Line Style
  • Filled
  • Line Visible
  • Rendering Style
  • Transparency
